{"tid":158914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【啟德新盤】業主馮生：大陸人來炒高哂","createTime":"2017-03-16T15:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T15:01:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"007e6fa342bbc83516b5edeb5d3ca70e63b73371","tid":158914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"已有樓的馮先生表示：「樓價狂癲，升得太離譜，與市民購買力脫節，根本普通打工仔萬零蚊一個月，無可能買到樓。如果有錢，有一幾千萬百都唔會去諗買樓，覺得唔值，香港樓係唔值咁嘅價錢。我覺得都是大陸人來炒高哂，買貴哂地皮，正常香港咁嘅環境，市民咁嘅收入，無可能咁嘅價錢，好似山頂6、7萬，10萬都話來緊頭，新蒲崗、深水埗都話萬幾兩萬蚊一呎，真是脫節!」<br />\n雖然有樓在手，但他坦言：「賣咗，買唔返，無理由由頭來過，俾三成首期，然後再供㗎。咁難得甩難，無理由mark鐘再起㗎!」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489666848_1644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489666848_1644.jpg&h=a59cbadc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170316/56438132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170316%2F56438132&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=27f0c9fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170316%2F56438132&h=35e97f94\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170316/56438132</a>"},{"pid":"73d29546af25291fd42ba699ce03d6fb32403931","tid":158914,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"無理由mark鐘再起㗎!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d0c2bb21d5f349469f6fb68d25f18f71b109d4","tid":158914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,